race.description: Silks Under The Stars Dec 19 Free Entry Hcp
race.comment: KETTLEBELL (4) resumes. She mixed her form last time in but was largely running in better races than this, measuring up decently well in town. This is a fairly moderate race and she can get away with it fresh. BACKSTAGE (1) resumes. Not sure 1000m is his go but he's run well over 1200m in better class than this and he does have some pace. If he's zippy enough he'll take some beating. DARLING TAKE CARE (5) broke through for a narrow maiden win at Ballina when last seen, tracking the speed and getting the upper hand late. All her form is at this trip and she maps for a very similar run here. XUANFENG (9) is fresh for this. He can mix his form a bit but is with a new yard here and has the ability on his day.
